title: Holiday Spectacular
itunes:title: Holiday Spectacular
description:
In this outrageous episode, the GOOD FOR YOU TEAM celebrates the festive season by answering your voicemails and giving advice. Whitney, Benton, and Emily argue about the best gifts (comedy), marriage, sex, and dog custody.  It's a holly jolly roller coaster--just like being home for the holidays.
